#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md
msgid "**Technical Debt**: The accumulated cost of taking shortcuts in software design. Like financial debt, a small amount can be productive (you ship faster now). A large amount becomes crippling (you spend all your time on interest payments, i.e., bug fixes and workarounds, instead of new features)."
msgstr ""

