#: src/foundations/fnd-004-engineering-infrastructure.md
msgid "A PR that moves 260,000 lines of code across 10 new crates, touching hundreds of files, puts this script in territory it was not designed for. The changed-file surface is too large for an incremental comparison to produce a meaningful signal. The script needs to understand workspace structure: specifically that a change to a file in `crates/zeroclaw-channels/` should be evaluated in the context of that crate, not the root."
msgstr ""

#: src/foundations/fnd-004-engineering-infrastructure.md
msgid "A PR touching only `zeroclaw-tool-call-parser` runs tests for that crate and its dependents, not the full workspace"
msgstr "`zeroclaw-tool-call-parser` のみを変更する PR は、ワークスペース全体のテストではなく、そのクレートとその依存関係のテストを実行します。"

